a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball I

p.k: The Robot / The Picnic / The Goons / The Secret Gumball discovers that Bobert is planning to take over his identity and replace him! / Gumball and Darwin barely survive a school picnic in the Forest of Doom. / Gumball sets out to win his Dad back by winning a blindfolded “dumb” race. / Gumball almost loses his mind trying to guess Darwin’s secret.
